title: Malaysia Digital X-Port Grant (MDXG)
description: Supports export-ready Malaysian tech companies to expand globally. Ceiling: up to RM1,000,000 depending on ownership structure. Duration: up to 1 year.
eligibility: Local-owned: ≥51% Malaysian equity, min share capital RM50k; Foreign-majority: HQ in Malaysia, min share capital RM500k. Must be in operation ≥1 year, Malaysia Digital/MSC status, ≥50% Malaysian team, generate export commercial value. Cannot owe MDEC clawbacks or be blacklisted.
requiredDocs: Pitch deck (MDEC template), audited financial statements (latest year), board resolution for signatory, company profile, outsourcing agreements (if applicable).
